# 必填
title: "Some strange feelings"
description: ""
pubDate: 2026-07-03T01:54:00
author: Kirishima
category: Vignettes
tags:
  - cognitive-dump
heroImage: ../../../../../../assets/2026-07-03-014010_1173_17.jpg
